data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER: True Country Living with beautiful 360 degree mountain views. This is a 3 bedrooms 2 bath 1728 sq. ft. home with a large 2 car garage with extra storage and an additional shop. Master bedroom has large soaking tub and separate shower. Kitchen has gas stovetop and wall oven.  Enclosed 260 sq. ft. front porch with ceiling fans.  Enclosed 360 sq. ft. recreational back room with views of the mountains. Plus a bonus/sewing/craft room. There is a lighted root cellar under the main garage. New tile in bathrooms and kitchen and new carpet throughout the main living areas. A new well pump and electrical box have recently been installed. This property sits on 1.98 Acres. Lot behind this property is also for sale 2.10 acres $22,000 10-0111-01
